title: 09/06/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 09/06/21 DPS Best Of
description:
Jonas Knox, Brady Quinn, and LaVar Arrington, in for Dan, react to a huge weekend in college football and highlight Notre Dame's overtime win at Florida State. The guys explain what sets apart Alabama and break down the expectations for Bryce Young this season. Did the Patriots lose a valuable mentor for Mac Jones after releasing Cam Newton? Plus, the guys react live to Tyrod Taylor being named the starter in Houston, as Deshaun Watson will sit on the bench.
